@startuml sequence-tc2-visitor-between-pois
title TC2 — Du khách giữa 2 POI: vị trí thiết bị → POI gần & hàng đợi audio

skinparam backgroundColor #0f1117
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #90caf9
    ActorBorderColor #90caf9
    ActorBackgroundColor #1a1d27
    ParticipantBorderColor #293043
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #171b27
    ParticipantFontColor #e0e0e0
    LifeLineBorderColor #293043
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #1a1d27
    NoteBackgroundColor #1a2a3a
    NoteBorderColor #293043
    NoteFontColor #aaa
}
skinparam defaultFontColor #e0e0e0

== Phần A: Admin web xem du khách đang ở giữa 2 POI ==

actor "Du khách\n(Android App)" as User
participant "DeviceHub\n(SignalR)" as Hub
database "GuestDevices\n(DB)" as DB
database "Pois\n(DB)" as PoiDB
participant "GET /nearby-pois\n(Program.cs)" as NearbyApi
actor "Admin Web\n(CMS)" as Admin

User -> Hub : SendLocation("DEV-001", lat=10.7798, lng=106.6991)
activate Hub
Hub -> DB : UPDATE GuestDevices\nSET LastLatitude=10.7798, LastLongitude=106.6991\nWHERE DeviceId="DEV-001"
DB --> Hub
deactivate Hub

note over DB
  Du khách đang ở giữa:
  • POI A: Nhà thờ Đức Bà (r=120m, dist=95m) ← trong vùng
  • POI B: Bưu điện TP (r=100m, dist=80m)  ← trong vùng
  • POI C: Chợ Bến Thành (r=150m, dist=380m) ← ngoài vùng, trong 500m
end note

Admin -> NearbyApi : GET /api/v1/admin/devices/DEV-001/nearby-pois
activate NearbyApi

NearbyApi -> DB : SELECT * FROM GuestDevices\nWHERE DeviceId = "DEV-001"
DB --> NearbyApi : { LastLatitude: 10.7798, LastLongitude: 106.6991 }

NearbyApi -> PoiDB : SELECT * FROM Pois WHERE IsActive = 1
PoiDB --> NearbyApi : [POI A, POI B, POI C, ...]

NearbyApi -> NearbyApi : foreach poi:\n  dist = HaversineDistance(10.7798, 106.6991,\n                           poi.Lat, poi.Lng)\n  withinRadius = dist <= poi.RadiusMeters\n  filter: dist <= 500

NearbyApi --> Admin : [\n  { poiId:1, name:"Nhà thờ Đức Bà",\n    distanceMeters:95, radiusMeters:120,\n    withinRadius:true },\n  { poiId:2, name:"Bưu điện TP HCM",\n    distanceMeters:80, radiusMeters:100,\n    withinRadius:true },\n  { poiId:3, name:"Chợ Bến Thành",\n    distanceMeters:380, radiusMeters:150,\n    withinRadius:false }\n]
deactivate NearbyApi

Admin -> Admin : showNearbyPois popup:\n● Nhà thờ Đức Bà  — 95m / r120m  [Trong vùng]\n● Bưu điện TP HCM — 80m / r100m  [Trong vùng]\n○ Chợ Bến Thành   — 380m / r150m [Ngoài vùng]

== Phần B: Hàng đợi audio khi nhiều du khách cùng vào POI ==

actor "Du khách 1\n(DEV-001)" as U1
actor "Du khách 2\n(DEV-002)" as U2
participant "AndroidGeofenceService" as Geo
participant "PoiNarrationHandler\n(debounce 250ms)" as Handler
participant "PoiNarrationRateLimiter\n(Semaphore/POI)" as Limiter
participant "NarrationManager\n(worker loop)" as NM
participant "Audio / TTS" as Audio

note over Limiter
  MaxConcurrentPerPoi = 10
  SpreadDelayMs = 80ms
end note

U1 -> Geo : OnEnter(POI A)
U2 -> Geo : OnEnter(POI A)

Geo -> Handler : HandlePoiEnterAsync(DEV-001, POI A)
Geo -> Handler : HandlePoiEnterAsync(DEV-002, POI A)

activate Handler
Handler -> Handler : debounce 250ms\n(gộp event nhanh)

Handler -> Limiter : AcquireAsync(poiId=1, "DEV-001")
activate Limiter
note right of Limiter
  SemaphoreSlim: currentCount > 0
  → cho phép DEV-001
end note
Limiter --> Handler : acquired (slot 1/10)
deactivate Limiter

Handler -> NM : Enqueue(DEV-001, POI A, Enter)
deactivate Handler

Handler -> Limiter : AcquireAsync(poiId=1, "DEV-002")
activate Limiter
note right of Limiter
  currentCount > 0
  Delay(80ms * 1)  ← spread để tránh đụng độ
  → cho phép DEV-002
end note
Limiter --> Handler : acquired (slot 2/10)
deactivate Limiter

Handler -> NM : Enqueue(DEV-002, POI A, Enter)

activate NM
NM -> NM : Sort queue: Tap(1) > Enter(2) > Near(3)\nDedup: IsDuplicate(poiId, deviceId, 2s)

NM -> Audio : PlayAudio(DEV-001, POI A)
note right of Audio
  DEV-001 nghe audio trước
end note
Audio --> NM : onEnded

NM -> Audio : PlayAudio(DEV-002, POI A)
note right of Audio
  DEV-002 vào hàng → nghe sau 80ms
end note
Audio --> NM : onEnded
deactivate NM

NM -> Limiter : Release(poiId=1, "DEV-001")
NM -> Limiter : Release(poiId=1, "DEV-002")

note over U1, Audio
  **Kết quả:**
  Cả 2 du khách đều nghe thuyết minh POI A
  theo thứ tự vào hàng, không xung đột
end note

@enduml
